This paper is about optimizing the computation of large neural networks on GPUs with limited memory. The paper focuses on deep learning, which is a subfield of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of GPUs for image recognition tasks (cs.CV), and the methods proposed in the paper involve optimizing the computation of neural networks (cs.NE) and considering the characteristics of each layer (cs.DC).
